metadata.name: The Sacrifice of Veritas
metadata.description:
"The Sacrifice of Veritas - A 21st Century Media Production" tackles the loss of truth  (embodied by the Roman goddess Veritas) in modern media society and the resulting social division. 

It is an artistic exploration - not a political statement!

Digital painting co-created by artificial intelligence.

300 dpi I 6.329 x 4.754
